Infratil net asset backing NZ $ 1 . 224 / share . Infrastructure and Utilities NZ Ltd ( Infratil ) said on Tuesday based on its unaudited management accounts as at December 31 1996 , its net asset backing , undiluted for options , was NZ $ 1 . 224 per fully paid share . " This value is calculated after taking into account the company ' s net income after tax and after deducting a provision for tax on unrealised gains on investments held by Infratil Securities Limited , " Infratil said in a statement . - - Wellington Newsroom ( 64 4 ) 4734746 
